{"id":4291,"date":"2025-06-19T11:58:33","date_gmt":"2025-06-19T04:58:33","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/?p=4291"},"modified":"2025-06-19T11:58:33","modified_gmt":"2025-06-19T04:58:33","slug":"sua-rua-mat-gsc-5-5-ph-cleansing-gel-co-tot-khong","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/thong-tin-nganh\/sua-rua-mat-gsc-5-5-ph-cleansing-gel-co-tot-khong\/","title":{"rendered":"S\u1eefa r\u1eeda m\u1eb7t GSC+ 5.5 pH Cleansing Gel c\u00f3 t\u1ed1t kh\u00f4ng?"},"content":{"rendered":"<p><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Trong chu tr\u00ecnh ch\u0103m s\u00f3c da, s\u1eefa r\u1eeda m\u1eb7t l\u00e0 b\u01b0\u1edbc kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 thi\u1ebfu \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u1eef l\u00e0n da s\u1ea1ch kh\u1ecfe, th\u00f4ng tho\u00e1ng v\u00e0 s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng h\u1ea5p th\u1ee5 d\u01b0\u1ee1ng ch\u1ea5t. Nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i lo\u1ea1i n\u00e0o c\u0169ng ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi m\u1ecdi lo\u1ea1i da. V\u1eady <\/span><\/i><b><i>s\u1eefa r\u1eeda m\u1eb7t GSC+ 5.5 pH Cleansing Gel <\/i><\/b><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">c\u00f3 t\u1ed1t kh\u00f4ng? N\u00ean d\u00f9ng v\u00e0o th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m n\u00e0o \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ea1t hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 t\u1ed1i \u01b0u? B\u00e0i vi\u1ebft sau s\u1ebd gi\u00fap b\u1ea1n gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u00e1p to\u00e0n b\u1ed9.<\/span><\/i><\/p>\n\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"sua-rua-mat-la-gi\"><\/span><b>S\u1eefa r\u1eeda m\u1eb7t l\u00e0 g\u00ec?<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">S\u1eefa r\u1eeda m\u1eb7t l\u00e0 s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m l\u00e0m s\u1ea1ch da chuy\u00ean d\u1ee5ng, c\u00f3 t\u00e1c d\u1ee5ng lo\u1ea1i b\u1ecf b\u1ee5i b\u1ea9n, b\u00e3 nh\u1eddn, t\u1ebf b\u00e0o ch\u1ebft, v\u00e0 c\u00e1c t\u1ea1p ch\u1ea5t t\u00edch t\u1ee5 tr\u00ean da sau m\u1ed9t ng\u00e0y d\u00e0i ti\u1ebfp x\u00fac v\u1edbi m\u00f4i tr\u01b0\u1eddng. Ngo\u00e0i c\u00f4ng d\u1ee5ng l\u00e0m s\u1ea1ch, nhi\u1ec1u d\u00f2ng s\u1eefa r\u1eeda m\u1eb7t ng\u00e0y nay c\u00f2n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u1ed5 sung th\u00eam c\u00e1c th\u00e0nh ph\u1ea7n d\u01b0\u1ee1ng \u1ea9m, ki\u1ec1m d\u1ea7u ho\u1eb7c h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 \u0111i\u1ec1u tr\u1ecb m\u1ee5n \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng t\u1eebng nhu c\u1ea7u da kh\u00e1c nhau.<\/span><\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"sua-rua-mat-co-tac-dung-gi\"><\/span><b>S\u1eeda r\u1eeda m\u1eb7t c\u00f3 t\u00e1c d\u1ee5ng g\u00ec?<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Vi\u1ec7c s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng s\u1eefa r\u1eeda m\u1eb7t \u0111\u00fang c\u00e1ch mang l\u1ea1i nhi\u1ec1u l\u1ee3i \u00edch thi\u1ebft th\u1ef1c:<\/span><\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_4369\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-4369\" style=\"width: 800px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img fetchpriority=\"high\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"size-full wp-image-4369\" src=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/59-1.webp\" alt=\"S\u1eeda r\u1eeda m\u1eb7t c\u00f3 t\u00e1c d\u1ee5ng g\u00ec\" width=\"800\" height=\"450\" srcset=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/59-1.webp 800w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/59-1-300x169.webp 300w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/59-1-768x432.webp 768w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/59-1-600x338.webp 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-4369\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">S\u1eeda r\u1eeda m\u1eb7t c\u00f3 t\u00e1c d\u1ee5ng g\u00ec<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<ul>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">L\u00e0m s\u1ea1ch s\u00e2u l\u1ed7 ch\u00e2n l\u00f4ng, lo\u1ea1i b\u1ecf c\u1eb7n b\u1ea9n gi\u00fap da th\u00f4ng tho\u00e1ng.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Gi\u1ea3m nguy c\u01a1 h\u00ecnh th\u00e0nh m\u1ee5n do b\u00edt t\u1eafc t\u1eeb d\u1ea7u th\u1eeba v\u00e0 t\u1ebf b\u00e0o ch\u1ebft.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">C\u00e2n b\u1eb1ng \u0111\u1ed9 pH t\u1ef1 nhi\u00ean cho da, gi\u1eef l\u1edbp m\u00e0ng \u1ea9m b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">T\u0103ng hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 h\u1ea5p th\u1ee5 d\u01b0\u1ee1ng ch\u1ea5t t\u1eeb c\u00e1c b\u01b0\u1edbc skincare ti\u1ebfp theo.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">H\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n k\u1ebft c\u1ea5u da, gi\u00fap da s\u00e1ng m\u1ecbn, \u0111\u1ec1u m\u00e0u h\u01a1n.<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"sua-rua-mat-gsc-55-ph-cleansing-gel-%e2%80%93-diu-nhe-an-toan-cho-da-nhay-cam\"><\/span><b>S\u1eefa r\u1eeda m\u1eb7t GSC 5.5 pH Cleansing Gel &#8211; D\u1ecbu nh\u1eb9, an to\u00e0n cho da nh\u1ea1y c\u1ea3m<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">V\u1edbi l\u00e0n da d\u1ec5 b\u1ecb k\u00edch \u1ee9ng, ch\u1ecdn s\u1eefa r\u1eeda m\u1eb7t d\u1ecbu nh\u1eb9 l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u ti\u00ean quy\u1ebft. GSC 5.5 pH Cleansing Gel ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 gi\u1ea3i ph\u00e1p l\u00fd t\u01b0\u1edfng nh\u1edd c\u00f4ng th\u1ee9c c\u00e2n b\u1eb1ng \u0111\u1ed9 pH \u1edf m\u1ee9c 5.5 &#8211; m\u1ee9c l\u00fd t\u01b0\u1edfng gi\u00fap b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 l\u1edbp m\u00e0ng \u1ea9m t\u1ef1 nhi\u00ean c\u1ee7a da, h\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf t\u00ecnh tr\u1ea1ng kh\u00f4 c\u0103ng sau khi r\u1eeda m\u1eb7t. K\u1ebft c\u1ea5u gel trong su\u1ed1t, t\u1ea1o b\u1ecdt nh\u1eb9 nh\u00e0ng, gi\u00fap l\u00e0m s\u1ea1ch s\u00e2u b\u1ee5i b\u1ea9n, d\u1ea7u th\u1eeba v\u00e0 t\u1ea1p ch\u1ea5t t\u1eeb l\u1ed7 ch\u00e2n l\u00f4ng m\u00e0 v\u1eabn gi\u1eef \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ed9 \u1ea9m m\u01b0\u1ee3t cho da.<\/span><\/p>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"tai-sao-nen-chon-gsc-55-ph-cleansing-gel\"><\/span><b><i>T\u1ea1i sao n\u00ean ch\u1ecdn GSC 5.5 pH Cleansing Gel?<\/i><\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">S\u1eefa r\u1eeda m\u1eb7t GSC 5.5 pH Cleansing Gel \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf d\u00e0nh ri\u00eang cho l\u00e0n da y\u1ebfu, da nh\u1ea1y c\u1ea3m v\u00e0 d\u1ec5 k\u00edch \u1ee9ng. V\u1edbi dung t\u00edch 150ml nh\u1ecf g\u1ecdn, ti\u1ec7n l\u1ee3i, s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m th\u00edch h\u1ee3p s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng t\u1ea1i nh\u00e0 ho\u1eb7c mang theo khi \u0111i du l\u1ecbch. \u0110\u1ed9 pH chu\u1ea9n 5.5 gi\u00fap duy tr\u00ec h\u00e0ng r\u00e0o b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 da, l\u00e0m s\u1ea1ch s\u00e2u m\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng g\u00e2y kh\u00f4 r\u00e1t, h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 c\u00e2n b\u1eb1ng l\u01b0\u1ee3ng d\u1ea7u n\u01b0\u1edbc t\u1ef1 nhi\u00ean tr\u00ean da.<\/span><\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_4370\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-4370\" style=\"width: 800px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"size-full wp-image-4370\" src=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/59-2.webp\" alt=\"T\u1ea1i sao n\u00ean ch\u1ecdn GSC 5.5 pH Cleansing Gel\" width=\"800\" height=\"450\" srcset=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/59-2.webp 800w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/59-2-300x169.webp 300w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/59-2-768x432.webp 768w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/59-2-600x338.webp 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-4370\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">T\u1ea1i sao n\u00ean ch\u1ecdn GSC 5.5 pH Cleansing Gel<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"cong-dung-va-uu-diem-noi-bat\"><\/span><b><i>C\u00f4ng d\u1ee5ng v\u00e0 \u01b0u \u0111i\u1ec3m n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt<\/i><\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<ul>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">L\u00e0m s\u1ea1ch b\u1ee5i b\u1ea9n, b\u00e3 nh\u1eddn v\u00e0 t\u1ebf b\u00e0o ch\u1ebft t\u1eeb s\u00e2u trong l\u1ed7 ch\u00e2n l\u00f4ng<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">C\u00e2n b\u1eb1ng pH l\u00fd t\u01b0\u1edfng cho da, gi\u00fap duy tr\u00ec \u0111\u1ed9 \u1ea9m t\u1ef1 nhi\u00ean<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Kh\u00e1ng khu\u1ea9n, kh\u00e1ng vi\u00eam, h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 t\u1ed1t cho da m\u1ee5n, da \u0111ang y\u1ebfu<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Ch\u1ee9a chi\u1ebft xu\u1ea5t th\u1ef1c v\u1eadt l\u00e0nh t\u00ednh nh\u01b0: tr\u00e0 xanh, l\u00f4 h\u1ed9i, c\u00e1m g\u1ea1o, \u0111\u1eadu xanh, m\u00eda \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng, c\u00e2y ph\u1ec9,&#8230; gi\u00fap l\u00e0m d\u1ecbu, nu\u00f4i d\u01b0\u1ee1ng v\u00e0 ph\u1ee5c h\u1ed3i da<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">T\u00e1c d\u1ee5ng ch\u1ed1ng oxy h\u00f3a, l\u00e0m s\u1ea1ch v\u00e0 t\u00e1i t\u1ea1o l\u00e0n da kh\u1ecfe m\u1ea1nh t\u1eebng ng\u00e0y<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"gsc-55-ph-cleansing-gel-co-tot-khong\"><\/span><b><i>GSC+ 5.5 pH Cleansing Gel c\u00f3 t\u1ed1t kh\u00f4ng?<\/i><\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">C\u00e2u tr\u1ea3 l\u1eddi l\u00e0: R\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t v\u1edbi da nh\u1ea1y c\u1ea3m v\u00e0 da m\u1ee5n.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">GSC+ 5.5 pH Cleansing Gel l\u00e0 d\u00f2ng s\u1eefa r\u1eeda m\u1eb7t d\u1ecbu nh\u1eb9 c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ed9 pH chu\u1ea9n 5.5, gi\u00fap l\u00e0m s\u1ea1ch da m\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng g\u00e2y kh\u00f4 c\u0103ng hay m\u1ea5t c\u00e2n b\u1eb1ng l\u1edbp m\u00e0ng \u1ea9m t\u1ef1 nhi\u00ean. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9 pH l\u00fd t\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111\u1ec3 b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 h\u1ec7 vi sinh tr\u00ean da, gi\u1ea3m nguy c\u01a1 k\u00edch \u1ee9ng v\u00e0 gi\u1eef cho da kh\u1ecfe m\u1ea1nh m\u1ed7i ng\u00e0y. V\u1edbi:<\/span><\/p>\n<ul>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">C\u00f4ng th\u1ee9c kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ee9a sulfate l\u00e0m s\u1ea1ch d\u1ecbu nh\u1eb9, ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p cho da nh\u1ea1y c\u1ea3m.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Chi\u1ebft xu\u1ea5t th\u1ef1c v\u1eadt l\u00e0nh t\u00ednh nh\u01b0 tr\u00e0 xanh, hoa c\u00fac\u00a0 gi\u00fap l\u00e0m d\u1ecbu da, kh\u00e1ng khu\u1ea9n nh\u1eb9.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">C\u00e2n b\u1eb1ng d\u1ea7u n\u01b0\u1edbc: L\u00e0m s\u1ea1ch hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng l\u00e0m da m\u1ea5t n\u01b0\u1edbc.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">D\u1ea1ng gel m\u1ecfng nh\u1eb9, t\u1ea1o b\u1ecdt m\u1ecbn, d\u1ec5 r\u1eeda tr\u00f4i, kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i c\u1ea3m gi\u00e1c nh\u1eddn r\u00edt.<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<figure id=\"attachment_4368\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-4368\" style=\"width: 1200px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"size-full wp-image-4368\" src=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/59-thumb.webp\" alt=\"GSC+ 5.5 pH Cleansing Gel c\u00f3 t\u1ed1t kh\u00f4ng\" width=\"1200\" height=\"750\" srcset=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/59-thumb.webp 1200w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/59-thumb-300x188.webp 300w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/59-thumb-1024x640.webp 1024w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/59-thumb-768x480.webp 768w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/59-thumb-600x375.webp 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-4368\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">GSC+ 5.5 pH Cleansing Gel c\u00f3 t\u1ed1t kh\u00f4ng<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Nh\u1edd \u0111\u00f3, s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m n\u00e0y r\u1ea5t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u01b0a chu\u1ed9ng b\u1edfi c\u00e1c chuy\u00ean gia da li\u1ec5u v\u00e0 spa t\u1ea1i H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 Vi\u1ec7t Nam.<\/span><\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"khi-dung-sua-rua-mat-khi-nao\"><\/span><b>Khi d\u00f9ng s\u1eefa r\u1eeda m\u1eb7t khi n\u00e0o?<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng s\u1eefa r\u1eeda m\u1eb7t c\u0169ng \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng l\u1edbn \u0111\u1ebfn hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 ch\u0103m s\u00f3c da. B\u1ea1n n\u00ean r\u1eeda m\u1eb7t:<\/span><\/p>\n<ul>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Bu\u1ed5i s\u00e1ng: \u0110\u1ec3 lo\u1ea1i b\u1ecf d\u1ea7u th\u1eeba ti\u1ebft ra trong \u0111\u00eam v\u00e0 l\u00e0m m\u1edbi l\u00e0n da.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Bu\u1ed5i t\u1ed1i: Sau khi t\u1ea9y trang, d\u00f9ng \u0111\u1ec3 l\u00e0m s\u1ea1ch s\u00e2u c\u1eb7n m\u1ef9 ph\u1ea9m, b\u1ee5i b\u1ea9n, b\u00e3 nh\u1eddn sau m\u1ed9t ng\u00e0y d\u00e0i.<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<figure id=\"attachment_4371\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-4371\" style=\"width: 800px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"size-full wp-image-4371\" src=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/59-3.webp\" alt=\"Khi d\u00f9ng s\u1eefa r\u1eeda m\u1eb7t khi n\u00e0o\" width=\"800\" height=\"450\" srcset=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/59-3.webp 800w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/59-3-300x169.webp 300w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/59-3-768x432.webp 768w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/59-3-600x338.webp 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-4371\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Khi d\u00f9ng s\u1eefa r\u1eeda m\u1eb7t khi n\u00e0o<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">\u0110\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t, kh\u00f4ng n\u00ean r\u1eeda m\u1eb7t qu\u00e1 2 l\u1ea7n\/ng\u00e0y v\u00ec c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 khi\u1ebfn da b\u1ecb kh\u00f4, k\u00edch \u1ee9ng v\u00e0 t\u0103ng ti\u1ebft d\u1ea7u ng\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ea1i.<\/span><\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"ket-luan\"><\/span><b>K\u1ebft lu\u1eadn<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">N\u1ebfu b\u1ea1n \u0111ang t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm m\u1ed9t s\u1eefa r\u1eeda m\u1eb7t d\u1ecbu nh\u1eb9, an to\u00e0n cho da d\u1ea7u m\u1ee5n, nh\u1ea1y c\u1ea3m th\u00ec GSC+ 5.5 pH Cleansing Gel l\u00e0 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn kh\u00f4ng n\u00ean b\u1ecf qua. S\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 gi\u00fap l\u00e0m s\u1ea1ch da hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 m\u00e0 c\u00f2n b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 h\u00e0ng r\u00e0o \u0111\u1ed9 \u1ea9m v\u00e0 gi\u1eef da lu\u00f4n m\u1ec1m m\u01b0\u1ee3t, kh\u1ecfe m\u1ea1nh t\u1eeb s\u00e2u b\u00ean trong.<\/span><\/p>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>V\u1eady s\u1eefa r\u1eeda m\u1eb7t GSC+ 5.5 pH Cleansing Gel c\u00f3 t\u1ed1t kh\u00f4ng? N\u00ean d\u00f9ng v\u00e0o th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m n\u00e0o \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ea1t hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 t\u1ed1i \u01b0u? B\u00e0i vi\u1ebft sau s\u1ebd gi\u00fap b\u1ea1n gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u00e1p to\u00e0n b\u1ed9.<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":7,"featured_media":4368,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"_acf_changed":false,"footnotes":""},"categories":[16],"tags":[],"class_list":["post-4291","post","type-post","status-publish","format-standard","has-post-thumbnail","hentry","category-thong-tin-nganh"],"acf":[],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/4291","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embedd